{
  "wishlist-pending": {
    "header": {
      "title": "❤️ Your Wishlist is Waiting!"
    },
    "body": {
      "content": "# Don’t Miss Out 🛒\n\nSome of your wishlist items are still not purchased.\n\n### Items:\n- 🛍️ **Product**: {{productName}}\n- 💵 **Price**: {{productPrice}}\n\n*Hurry before the stock runs out or the offer ends!*",
      "type": "markdown",
      "image": {
        "uri": "{{wishlistImageUrl}}",
        "alt": "Wishlist preview"
      }
    },
    "footer": {
      "buyNow": {
        "text": "💳 Buy Now",
        "type": "navigation",
        "action": "open_wishlist",
        "actionType": "open_product",
